        dc:description           "Fig. 2.—Dorsal, ventral, and lateral views of skull and lateral view of the right mandible of an adult female Microtus cabrerae (Museu Bocage—National Museum of Natural History, Lisbon, Portugal, specimen MB01-001208) collected in Grandola, Portugal (38880N, 88330W) by Inês Rosário on 17 June 2004, donated by Maria da Luz Mathias. Greatest length of skull is 29.8 mm." ;
